name: COZY ROOM C
description:
[COZY ROOM COLLECTION - Regular]

| 2022 International Women's Day Edition |

A cozy room is a place where I can be myself without anyone putting labels and belittling me. When people underestimate me with their discouraging words, I stand firmly on my ground and push through every barrier in front of me. This room has witnessed me overcome a lot of challenges in the past, it is a place where I fight for my dream.

Original art and animation by 196 Pixels Light
